    <fr:title text="a working OCaml 5 installation">a working OCaml 5 installation</fr:title>
    <fr:taxon>Requirement</fr:taxon>
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
    <html:p><fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/forester/index.xml" title="Forester" addr="forest://forester/index" type="local">Forester</fr:link> is written in the <fr:link href="https://www.ocaml.org/" type="external">OCaml</fr:link> programming language, and makes use of the latest features of OCaml 5. Most users should install <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/forester/index.xml" title="Forester" addr="forest://forester/index" type="local">Forester</fr:link> through OCaml's <fr:link href="https://opam.ocaml.org/" type="external">opam</fr:link> package manager; instructions to install opam and OCaml simultaneously can be found <fr:link href="https://opam.ocaml.org/" type="external">here</fr:link>.</html:p>
  </fr:mainmatter>
